    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Without Questions in life what is the need for a Guru?  &lt;br&gt;
If my questions are well defined then do I need a Guru?  &lt;br&gt;
Guru helps in defining questions well  &lt;br&gt;
or answering whatever you ask?  &lt;br&gt;
Does he empower you by giving more information  &lt;br&gt;
or make you restless by holding half answer?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
